• Use [color=cyan]Arrow Keys[/color] or [color=cyan]WASD[/color] to move
• Collect all dots to advance to the next level
• Eat power pellets to make ghosts vulnerable
• Press [color=cyan]Space[/color] to dash (if unlocked)
• When you die, choose an upgrade to become stronger!

[color=yellow]Upgrades:[/color]
[color=red]❤[/color] Extra Life                    [color=orange]⚡[/color] Speed Boost
